[[File:Carbon_nanotubes_(CNTs)_combine_to_membrane.jpg|thumb]]
{{Nanomaterials}}
有很多'''生产碳纳米管的技术'''，包括电弧放电、激光烧蚀、高压一氧化碳歧化和[[化学气相沉积|化学气相沉积（CVD）]]。这些过程大多是在真空或工艺气体{{efn|例如，[[氦气|氦气]]就是一种在工业中广泛使用的惰性气体。}}中进行的。碳纳米管的CVD生长{{efn|CVD生长是将基底暴露在一种或多种不同的前趋物下，在基底表面发生化学反应或化学分解来产生沉积碳纳米管。}}可以在真空或大气压下进行，这些方法可以合成大量的碳纳米管。催化和连续生长方面的进步使碳纳米管的合成成本更加低。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=K. Takeuchi |coauthors=T. Hayashi, Y. A. Kim, K. Fujisawa, M. Endo |title=The state-of-the-art science and applications of carbon nanotubes |date=2014-02 |volume=5 |issue=1 |pages=15 |url=http://nanojournal.ifmo.ru/en/articles-2/volume5/5-1/paper01/ |accessdate=2016-05-14 |location=俄罗斯 |language=en |journal= |archive-date=2021-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427041356/http://nanojournal.ifmo.ru/en/articles-2/volume5/5-1/paper01/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 方法 ==

=== 电弧放电 ===
1991年，在100安培的电弧放电过程中，在石墨[[电极|电极]]的碳烟尘中观察到了碳纳米管，尽管其目的是为了产生[[富勒烯|富勒烯]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|first=Sumio|last=Iijima|year=1991|title=Helical microtubules of graphitic carbon|journal=Nature|volume=354|pages=56–58|doi=10.1038/354056a0|issue=6348|bibcode = 1991Natur.354...56I }}</ref>然而，1992年，[[日本電氣|日本電氣]]基础研究实验室的两位研究人员首次从[[宏观|宏观]]上生产出了碳纳米管<ref>{{Cite journal|first=T. W.|last=Ebbesen|year=1992|title=Large-scale synthesis of carbon nanotubes|journal=Nature|volume=358|pages=220–222|doi=10.1038/358220a0|last2=Ajayan|first2=P. M.|issue=6383|bibcode = 1992Natur.358..220E }}</ref>。他们同样使用了高安培电弧放电。在这个过程中，由于放电温度较高，负极中含有的碳会升华。

这种方法的产率按重量计可达30%。它能生产出长度达50微米的单壁和多壁纳米管且结构缺陷少。<ref name="nanotubes for electronics">{{cite journal|last=Collins |first=P.G.|year=2000|title=Nanotubes for Electronics|journal=[[科学美国人|Scientific American]]|volume=283|issue=6|pages=67–6|doi=10.1038/scientificamerican1200-62 |bibcode=2000SciAm.283f..62C|pmid=11103460}}</ref>与其他方法相比，电弧放电技术在较高的温度（1700℃以上）进行碳纳米管合成，通常能使其膨胀，结构缺陷少。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Eatemadi | first1 = Ali | last2 = Daraee | first2 = Hadis | last3 = Karimkhanloo | first3 = Hamzeh | last4 = Kouhi | first4 = Mohammad | last5 = Zarghami | first5 = Nosratollah | last6 = Akbarzadeh | first6 = Abolfazl | last7 = Abasi | first7 = Mozhgan | last8 = Hanifehpour | first8 = Younes | last9 = Woo Joo | first9 = Sang | year = 2014 | title = Carbon nanotubes: properties, synthesis, purification, and medical applications | url = | journal = Nanoscale Research Letters | volume = 9 | issue = 1| pages = 1–13 | bibcode = 2014NRL.....9....1L | doi = 10.1186/1556-276X-9-1 | pmid = 24380376 | pmc = 3895740 }}</ref>

=== 激光烧蚀 ===
在激光烧蚀中，[[脉冲激光器|脉冲激光]]在高温反应器中汽化石墨靶，同时将[[非活性氣體|惰性气体]]引入反应室。当汽化的碳冷凝时，纳米管在反应器的冷却表面上形成。系统中可包括水冷表面以收集纳米管。

这个过程是由[[萊斯大學|萊斯大學]]的[[理查德·斯莫利|理查德·斯莫利]]博士和同事开发的，在发现碳纳米管的时候，他们正在用激光对金属进行爆破，以产生各种金属分子。当他们听说纳米管的存在时，他们用石墨代替金属，制造出多壁碳纳米管。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Guo|first=Ting|title=Self-Assembly of Tubular Fullerenes|url=http://www.pa.msu.edu/cmp/csc/eprint/DT085.pdf|year=1995|journal=J. Phys. Chem.|volume=99|pages=10694–10697|doi=10.1021/j100027a002|last2=Nikolaev|first2=Pavel|last3=Rinzler|first3=Andrew G.|last4=Tomanek|first4=David|last5=Colbert|first5=Daniel T.|last6=Smalley|first6=Richard E.|issue=27|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808213722/http://www.pa.msu.edu/cmp/csc/eprint/DT085.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 当年晚些时候，该团队使用石墨和金属催化剂颗粒的复合体来合成单壁碳纳米管，而[[钴|钴]]和[[镍|镍]]的混合物催化剂产率最高<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Guo |first=Ting |title=Catalytic growth of single-walled nanotubes by laser vaporization |journal=Chem. Phys. Lett. |year=1995 |volume=243 |pages=49–54 |url=http://www.orgchem.science.ru.nl/molmat/mm-web/education/caput-college/ChemPhysLett-1995-243-49.pdf |doi=10.1016/0009-2614(95)00825-O |last2=Nikolaev |first2=P |last3=Thess |first3=A |last4=Colbert |first4=D |last5=Smalley |first5=R |bibcode=1995CPL...243...49B |issue=1–2 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724164437/http://www.orgchem.science.ru.nl/molmat/mm-web/education/caput-college/ChemPhysLett-1995-243-49.pdf |archive-date=24 July 2011 }}</ref>

激光烧蚀法的产率在70%左右，主要为单壁碳纳米管。碳纳米管的直径由反应温度决定。它比电弧放电或化学气相沉积都要贵。<ref name="nanotubes for electronics" />

在知道碳纳米管介质的空间调制折射率的情况下，由半导体碳纳米管的导带电子的玻尔兹曼无碰撞方程可以获得很少的循环光脉冲动力学的有效方程解。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://nanojournal.ifmo.ru/en/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/NPCM55P644.pdf|title=Few cycle pulses in the bragg medium containing carbon nanotubes|author=M.B. Belonenko|journal=Nanosystems: Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics|volume=14|issue=5|page=644|year=2014|display-authors=etal|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220030621/http://nanojournal.ifmo.ru/en/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/NPCM55P644.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 热等离子体法 ===
[[File:Plasma_torch_close_up.jpg|thumb]]
单壁碳纳米管也可以通过热等离子体法合成，该方法由Olivier Smiljanic于2000年在加拿大瓦伦尼斯的{{tsl|en|Institut national de la recherche scientifique|国家科学研究所}}首次发明。这种方法重现了电弧放电和激光烧蚀方法中普遍存在的条件，但使用含碳气体代替石墨蒸汽来提供必要的碳元素。这样做，单壁碳纳米管的生长效率更高，分解气体所消耗的能量可以比石墨蒸发少10倍。这个过程也可连续进行且成本较低。氩、乙烯和[[二茂铁|二茂铁]]的气态混合物加入微波等离子体炬中，在大气压等离子体的作用下雾化，形成强烈 "火焰"形态。“火焰”产生的烟雾中含有碳纳米管、金属和碳纳米粒子以及无定形碳。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Smiljanic|first=Olivier|first2=B.L. |last2=Stansfield|first3=J.-P. |last3=Dodelet|first4=A. |last4=Serventi|first5=S. |last5=Désilets|title=Gas-phase synthesis of SWNT by an atmospheric pressure plasma jet|journal=Chemical Physics Letters|date=22 April 2002|volume=356|issue=3–4|pages=189–193|doi=10.1016/S0009-2614(02)00132-X|bibcode=2002CPL...356..189S}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Smiljanic|first=Olivier|title=Method and apparatus for producing single-wall carbon nanotubes|url=http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&Sect2=HITOFF&p=1&u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-bool.html&r=4&f=G&l=50&co1=AND&d=PTXT&s1=7,591,989&OS=7,591,989&RS=7,591,989|work=US Patent|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2019-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212131214/http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO2&Sect2=HITOFF&p=1&u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsearch-bool.html&r=4&f=G&l=50&co1=AND&d=PTXT&s1=7,591,989&OS=7,591,989&RS=7,591,989|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另一种用等离子炬生产单壁碳纳米管的方法是使用{{tsl|en|Induction plasma|感应热等离子体法}}，该方法由舍布鲁克大学和加拿大国家研究委员会于2005年发现。<ref name="Large-scale production">{{Cite journal |title=Large-scale production of single-wall carbon nanotubes by induction thermal plasma |last=Kim |first=K.S. |last2=Cota-Sanchez |first2=German |journal=Journal of Physics D: Applied Physics |issue=8 |doi=10.1088/0022-3727/40/8/S17 |year=2007 |volume=40 |pages=2375–2387 |bibcode=2007JPhD...40.2375K |last3=Kingston |first3=Chris |last4=Imris |first4=M. |last5=Simard |first5=Benoît |last6=Soucy |first6=Gervais}}</ref> 该方法与电弧放电类似，因为两者都利用电离气体达到汽化含碳物质和随后纳米管生长所需的金属催化剂的高温。 热等离子体是由线圈中的高频振荡电流产生的，并在流动的惰性气体中维持。 通常，将炭黑和金属催化剂颗粒的原料加入等离子体中，然后冷却以合成不同直径的单壁碳纳米管。

感应热等离子体法每分钟可生产多达2克的纳米管材料，高于电弧放电法或激光烧蚀法。<ref name="Large-scale production"/>

=== 化学气相沉积 ===
[[Image:PICT0111.JPG|thumb]]
碳的催化气相沉积技术在1952年<ref name="CVD">{{cite journal|last=Радушкевич|first=Л. В.|year=1952|script-title=ru:О Структуре Углерода, Образующегося При Термическом Разложении Окиси Углерода На Железном Контакте|journal=Журнал Физической Химии|volume=26|pages=88–95|url=http://nanotube.msu.edu/HSS/2006/4/2006-4.pdf|language=ru|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305060142/http://nanotube.msu.edu/HSS/2006/4/2006-4.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>和1959年<ref>{{Cite journal|first=P. L.|last=Walker Jr.|journal=J. Phys. Chem.|volume=63|pages=133–140|year=1959|title=Carbon Formation from Carbon Monoxide-Hydrogen Mixtures over Iron Catalysts. I. Properties of Carbon Formed|doi=10.1021/j150572a002|last2=Rakszawski|first2=J. F.|last3=Imperial|first3=G. R.|issue=2}}</ref>就已经被发现并发表，但直到1993年才通过这种方法合成了碳纳米管。<ref>{{Cite journal|first=M.|last=José-Yacamán|title=Catalytic growth of carbon microtubules with fullerene structure|journal=Appl. Phys. Lett.|volume=62|page=657|year=1993|doi=10.1063/1.108857|last2=Miki-Yoshida|first2=M.|last3=Rendón|first3=L.|last4=Santiesteban|first4=J. G.|issue=6|bibcode = 1993ApPhL..62..657J }}</ref> 2007年，[[辛辛纳提大學|辛辛纳提大學]]的研究人员开发了一种在FirstNano ET3000碳纳米管生长系统上生长长度为18mm的对齐碳纳米管阵列的工艺。<ref>{{Cite news|title=UC Researchers Shatter World Records with Length of Carbon Nanotube Arrays|date=27 April 2007|last=Beckman|first=Wendy|publisher=University of Cincinnati|url=http://www.uc.edu/news/NR.asp?id=5700|accessdate=2020-11-26|archive-date=2009-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202112429/http://www.uc.edu/news/NR.asp?id=5700|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在CVD过程中，用金属催化剂颗粒层（最常见的是[[镍|镍]]，[[钴|钴]]，[[铁|铁]]或它们的组合<ref>
{{cite journal|title=Synthesis-condition dependence of carbon nanotube growth by alcohol catalytic chemical vapor deposition method|journal=Sci. Technol. Adv. Mater.|volume=8|year=2007|pages=292–295|doi=10.1016/j.stam.2007.02.009|last1=Inami|first1=Nobuhito|last2=Ambri Mohamed|first2=Mohd|last3=Shikoh|first3=Eiji|last4=Fujiwara|first4=Akihiko|issue=4|bibcode = 2007STAdM...8..292I |doi-access=free}}</ref>）制备衬底。[6]金属纳米颗粒也可以通过其他方式生产，包括还原氧化物或氧化物固溶体。在衬底表面生长的纳米管的直径与金属颗粒的尺寸有关。这可以通过金属的图案化（或掩膜）沉积，退火或金属层的等离子蚀刻来控制。在合成过程中基板需要加热到约700°C。工艺气体{{efn|例如[[氨|氨]]，[[氮|氮]]或[[氢|氢]]}}和含碳气体{{efn|例如[[乙炔|乙炔]]，[[乙烯|乙烯]]，[[乙醇|乙醇]]或[[甲烷|甲烷]]}}加入反应器后，碳纳米管在金属催化剂的位置上开始生长。含碳气体在催化剂颗粒的表面被分解，并且碳被运输到颗粒的边缘形成纳米管。该过程的机理仍在研究中。<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Naha, Sayangdev |author2=Ishwar K. Puri|title=A model for catalytic growth of carbon nanotubes|journal=Journal of Physics D: Applied Physics|volume= 41|issue=6|year=2008|doi=10.1088/0022-3727/41/6/065304|page= 065304|bibcode = 2008JPhD...41f5304N }}</ref>催化剂颗粒可以在生长过程中停留在正在生长的纳米管的顶端，也可以停留在基体上，具体取决于催化剂颗粒与基底之间的附着力。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Banerjee, Soumik, Naha, Sayangdev, and Ishwar K. Puri|title=Molecular simulation of the carbon nanotube growth mode during catalytic synthesis|journal=Applied Physics Letters|volume= 92|issue=23|year=2008|doi=10.1063/1.2945798|page= 233121|bibcode = 2008ApPhL..92w3121B |hdl=10919/47394|hdl-access=free}}</ref>碳氢化合物在催化剂下的热解已成为研究的一个活跃领域，并且可能成为大量生产碳纳米管的途径。流化床反应器是碳纳米管制备中应用最广泛的反应器。扩大其反应堆规模是研究人员的主要挑战。<ref>{{cite journal|last1 = Pinilla|first1 = JL|last2 = Moliner|first2 = R| year = 2007|last3 = Suelves|first3 = I|last4 = Lazaro|first4 = M|last5 = Echegoyen|first5 = Y|last6 = Palacios|first6 = J|title = Production of hydrogen and carbon nanofibers by thermal decomposition of methane using metal catalysts in a fluidized bed reactor|journal = International Journal of Hydrogen Energy|volume = 32|issue = 18| pages = 4821–4829|doi = 10.1016/j.ijhydene.2007.08.013}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1 = Muradov|first1 = N|year = 2001|title = Hydrogen via methane decomposition: an application for decarbonization of fossil fuels|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_international-journal-of-hydrogen-energy_2001-11_26_11/page/1165|journal = International Journal of Hydrogen Energy|volume = 26|issue = 11|pages = 1165–1175| doi= 10.1016/S0360-3199(01)00073-8}}</ref>

生产碳纳米管大部分使用化学气相沉积法。<ref>{{Cite journal|first=M.|last=Kumar|title=Chemical vapor deposition of carbon nanotubes: a review on growth mechanism and mass production.|journal=Journal of Nanoscience and Nanotechnology|volume=10|page=6|year=2010|doi=10.1166/jnn.2010.2939|issue=6|citeseerx=10.1.1.459.5003}}</ref>将金属纳米颗粒与催化剂载体如MgO或Al<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>混合以增加表面积，可使碳原料与金属颗粒的催化反应产率更高。这种合成路线的一个问题是通过酸处理去除催化剂载体，有时可能会破坏碳纳米管的原始结构。然而，可溶于水的替代催化剂载体已被证明对纳米管的生长是有效的。<ref>{{Cite journal|first=A.|last=Eftekhari|title=High-yield synthesis of carbon nanotubes using a water-soluble catalyst support in catalytic chemical vapor deposition|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_carbon_2006-06_44_7/page/1343|doi=10.1016/j.carbon.2005.12.006|journal=Carbon|volume=44|pages=1343-1345|year=2006|last2=Jafarkhani|first2=P|last3=Moztarzadeh|first3=F|issue=7}}</ref>

如果在碳纳米管生长过程中施加强电场产生[[等离子体|等离子体]]{{efn|如本章节附图所示，等离子体态可增强化学气相沉积程度}}，则纳米管的生长方向将与电场方向相同。<ref>{{Cite journal| title=Synthesis of Large Arrays of Well-Aligned Carbon Nanotubes on Glass| journal=Science| volume=282| year=1998| doi=10.1126/science.282.5391.1105| pmid=9804545| issue=5391| pages=1105–7| last1=Ren| first1=Z. F.| last2=Huang| first2=ZP| last3=Xu| first3=JW| last4=Wang| first4=JH| last5=Bush| first5=P| last6=Siegal| first6=MP| last7=Provencio| first7=PN| bibcode=1998Sci...282.1105R| url=https://digital.library.unt.edu/ark:/67531/metadc668971/| type=Submitted manuscript| access-date=2020-11-26| archive-date=2020-12-03| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203180530/https://digital.library.unt.edu/ark:/67531/metadc668971/| dead-url=no}}</ref>通过调整反应器的几何形状，可以合成{{tsl|en|Vertically aligned carbon nanotube arrays|垂直排列的碳纳米管}}<ref>{{Cite web |title=SEM images & TEM images of carbon nanotubes, aligned carbon nanotube arrays, and nanoparticles |url=http://www.nano-lab.com/imagegallery.html |accessdate=2020-11-27 |author=Nano-lab.com. |date=2005 |format=.jpg/.jpeg |publisher=Nano-lab.com. |language=en |archive-date=2017-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113163933/http://www.nano-lab.com/imagegallery.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>（即垂直于基底）。 如果不使用等离子体，产物取向将无法确定。 在某些反应条件下，即使没有等离子体，间距紧密的碳纳米管也会保持垂直生长方向，从而形成类似地毯或森林的密集管阵。

在各种合成碳纳米管的方法中，CVD最有希望实现工业规模化沉积。它的价格/单位比较低，并且CVD能够直接在所需的基底上生长，而其他生长技术必须分离并提纯纳米管。 特殊沉积方式产生的催化剂的碳纳米管生长位点可控。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Synthesis and field emission properties of vertically aligned carbon nanotube arrays on copper|journal=Carbon|volume=50|year=2012|doi=10.1016/j.carbon.2012.02.024|issue=7|pages=2641–50| last1=Neupane| first1=Suman| last2=Lastres| first2=Mauricio| last3=Chiarella| first3=M| last4=Li| first4=W.Z.| last5=Su| first5=Q| last6=Du| first6=G.H.}}</ref>2007年，[[名城大學|名城大學]]的一个团队演示了一种[[樟腦|樟腦]]中生长碳纳米管的高效CVD技术。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Carbon Nanotubes from Camphor: An Environment-Friendly Nanotechnology|journal=Journal of Physics: Conference Series|volume=61|issue=1|year=2007| pages=643–646|doi = 10.1088/1742-6596/61/1/129|last1=Kumar|first1=Mukul|last2=Ando|first2=Yoshinori|bibcode = 2007JPhCS..61..643K |doi-access=free}}</ref>[[萊斯大學|萊斯大學]]的研究人员由[[理查德·斯莫利|理查德·斯莫利]]（{{lang|en|Richard Smalley}}）领导，一直致力于寻找生产大量、纯净、特定类型的碳纳米管的方法。 他们的方法是从单根纳米管上切下许多小种子生长出长纤维，结果发现所有长纤维的直径与原始纳米管的直径相同，类型也可能相同。<ref name="SmalleyLi2006">{{cite journal|last1=Smalley|first1=Richard E.|last2=Li|first2=Yubao|last3=Moore|first3=Valerie C.|last4=Price|first4=B. Katherine|last5=Colorado|first5=Ramon|last6=Schmidt|first6=Howard K.|last7=Hauge|first7=Robert H.|last8=Barron|first8=Andrew R.|last9=Tour|first9=James M.|title=Single Wall Carbon Nanotube Amplification: En Route to a Type-Specific Growth Mechanism|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=128|issue=49|year=2006|pages=15824–15829|doi=10.1021/ja065767r|pmid=17147393}}</ref>

==== 超增长气相沉积 ====
超增长CVD（水辅助化学气相沉积）是由日本{{tsl|en|National Institute of Advanced Industrial Science and Technology|国立先进产业科学技术研究所}}的羽田贤治、[[饭岛澄男|饭岛澄男]]和他的同事开发的。<ref>
{{cite journal|title=Water-Assisted Highly Efficient Synthesis of Impurity-Free Single-Walled Carbon Nanotubes|journal=Science |volume=306 |pages=1362–1365 |year=2004 |doi=10.1126/science.1104962 |pmid=15550668 |issue=5700|last1=Hata |first1=K. |last2=Futaba |first2=DN |last3=Mizuno |first3=K |last4=Namai |first4=T |last5=Yumura |first5=M |last6=Iijima |first6=S|bibcode = 2004Sci...306.1362H |citeseerx=10.1.1.467.9078 }}</ref>在该方法中，向CVD反应器中加入水可显著提高催化剂的活性和寿命。反应器中产生了垂直于基材排列的致密的毫米高垂直排列的纳米管阵列。这些阵列的高度方程可表示为：

: <math> H(t) = {\beta}{\tau}_o ({1 - e^{-t / {\tau}_o}}).</math><ref name="relationship">{{cite journal |author1=CHEN GUOHAI |coauthors=R. C. Davis, H. Kimura, S. Sakurai, M. Yumura, D. N. Futaba and K. Hata |title=The relationship between the growth rate and the lifetime in carbon nanotube synthesis |journal=Nanoscale |date=2015 |volume=7 |issue=19 |pages=8873-8878 |doi=10.1039/C5NR01125F |url=https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2015/NR/C5NR01125F#!divAbstract |accessdate=2020-11-29 |publisher=Nanoscale |location=英国 |language=en |format=pdf |issn=2040-3372 |quote=We found that the increased growth temperature led to increased CNT growth rate and shortened catalyst lifetime for all carbon feedstocks, following an inverse relationship of a fairly constant maximum height. |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210121523/https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlelanding/2015/NR/C5NR01125F#!divAbstract |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在该方程中，β代表碳纳米管的生长速率，<math> {\tau}_o </math>代表催化剂特征寿命。<ref>
{{cite journal |title=Kinetics of Water-Assisted Single-Walled Carbon Nanotube Synthesis Revealed by a Time-Evolution Analysis |journal=Phys. Rev. Lett. |volume=95 |page=056104 |year=2005 |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.95.056104 |issue=5 |last1=Futaba |first1=Don |last2=Hata |first2=Kenji |last3=Yamada |first3=Takeo |last4=Mizuno |first4=Kohei |last5=Yumura |first5=Motoo |last6=Iijima |first6=Sumio|bibcode = 2005PhRvL..95e6104F |pmid=16090893}}</ref>

其比表面积超过1000 m<sup>2</sup>/g（封顶）或2200 m<sup>2</sup>/g（无封顶）<ref name="Compact and light supercapacitors">{{Cite journal |title=Compact and light supercapacitors from a surface-only solid by opened carbon nanotubes with 2,200 m<sup>2</sup>/g |first=Tatsuki |last2=Izadi-Najafabadi |first2=Ali |journal=[[先进功能材料|Advanced Functional Materials]] |issue=3 |doi=10.1002/adfm.200901927 |year=2009 |volume=20 |pages=422–428 |last3=Yamada |first3=Takeo |last4=Futaba |first4=Don N. |last5=Yasuda |first5=Satoshi |last6=Tanaike |first6=Osamu |last7=Hatori |first7=Hiroaki |last8=Yumura |first8=Motoo |last9=Iijima |first9=Sumio |display-authors=8 |last1=Hiraoka |last10=Hata |first10=Kenji}}</ref>，超过了HiPco样品400-1,000 m<sup>2</sup>/g的表现。<ref>{{cite web|title=Unidym product sheet SWNT |url=http://www.unidym.com/files/Unidym_Product_Sheet_SWNT.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717162816/http://www.unidym.com/files/Unidym_Product_Sheet_SWNT.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-date=2011-07-17 }}</ref>超增长气相沉积合成效率是{{tsl|en|laser ablation|激光烧蚀}}法的100倍左右。2004年，用该方法制造高度为2.5mm的单壁碳纳米管“森林”所需时间为10分钟。该方法得到的产物容易从催化剂中分离，纯度>99.98%，无需进一步提纯；而在相同条件下生长的HiPco碳纳米管含有大约5-35%的金属杂质。超增长技术避免了分离与离心提纯所导致碳纳米管的损坏。该方法同样可以制造图案化的高组织单壁碳纳米管结构。<ref name="Compact and light supercapacitors"/>

超增长碳纳米管的[[密度|密度]]约为0.037 g/cm<sup>3</sup>。<ref>{{cite web|title=Characteristic of Carbon nanotubes by super-growth method|language=ja|url=http://www.nanocarbon.jp/sg/002.html|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2009-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091213194910/http://www.nanocarbon.jp/sg/002.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="K.Hata">{{cite web|author=K.Hata|title=From Highly Efficient Impurity-Free CNT Synthesis to DWNT forests, CNTsolids and Super-Capacitors|url=http://www.nanocarbon.jp/english/research/image/review.pdf|access-date=2020-11-26|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215122421/http://nanocarbon.jp/english/research/image/review.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>它远低于传统的碳纳米管粉末（〜1.34 g/cm<sup>3</sup>），可能是因为后者包含金属和[[无定形碳|无定形碳]]。

超生长法是化学气相沉积法的一种变体，可以生长含有单壁碳纳米管、双壁碳纳米管和多壁碳纳米管的材料，并通过调整生长条件来改变它们的比例。<ref>
{{cite journal |title=Size-selective growth of double-walled carbon nanotube forests from engineered iron catalysts |journal={{tsl|en|Nature Nanotechnology||Nature Nanotechnology}} |volume=1 |pages=131–136 |year=2006|doi=10.1038/nnano.2006.95 |pmid=18654165 |issue=2 |last1=Yamada |first1=Takeo |last2=Namai |first2=Tatsunori |last3=Hata |first3=Kenji |last4=Futaba |first4=Don N. |last5=Mizuno |first5=Kohei |last6=Fan |first6=Jing
 |last7=Yudasaka |first7=Masako |last8=Yumura |first8=Motoo |last9=Iijima |first9=Sumio|bibcode = 2006NatNa...1..131Y }}</ref> 它们的比例会因催化剂的厚度而改变。管的直径很宽，因其包含多壁碳纳米管。<ref name="K.Hata"/>

垂直排列的纳米管森林将其浸入溶剂中并干燥后，会产生“拉链效应”。拉链效应是由溶剂的表面张力和碳纳米管之间的范德华力引起的。 它将纳米管排列成致密的材料，通过在此过程中施加较小的压力，可以将其制成各种形状，例如片状和条状。 致密化使维氏硬度提高约70倍，密度为0.55 g/cm<sup>3</sup>。 堆积后的碳纳米管长度超过1毫米，并且碳纯度为99.9％或更高； 它们还保留了纳米管森林所需的排列特性。<ref>
{{cite journal|title=Shape-engineerable and highly densely packed single-walled carbon nanotubes and their application as super-capacitor electrodes |journal={{tsl|en|Nature Materials||Nature Materials}} |volume=5 |pages=987–994 |year=2006 |doi=10.1038/nmat1782 |pmid=17128258 |issue=12 |last1=Futaba |first1=Don N. |last2=Hata |first2=Kenji |last3=Yamada |first3=Takeo |last4=Hiraoka |first4=Tatsuki |last5=Hayamizu |first5=Yuhei |last6=Kakudate |first6=Yozo |last7=Tanaike|first7=Osamu |last8=Hatori|first8=Hiroaki |last9=Yumura |first9=Motoo|last10=Iijima |first10=Sumio |bibcode = 2006NatMa...5..987F |display-authors=8 }}</ref>

与多壁碳纳米管相比，单壁碳纳米管的低生长效率使其生产成本高；而超增长技术为单壁碳纳米管的商业化提供了一个机会。<ref name="super-growth method">{{cite journal |author1=Kenji HATA |authorlink1=羽田贤治 |title=A super-growth method for single-walled carbon nanotube synthesis — Development of a mass production technique for industrial application — |journal=Synthesiology |date=2016 |volume=9 |issue=3 |pages=165-177 |doi=10.5571/synth.9.3_165 |url=https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/synth/9/3/9_165/_article |accessdate=2020-11-28 |series=Super-growth CVD, single-walled CNT |publisher=J-STAGE |location=日本 |language=ja |format=pdf |issn=1882-6229}}</ref>

=== 液体电解法 ===
2015年，乔治华盛顿大学的研究人员发现了通过熔融碳酸盐电解合成多壁碳纳米管的新途径。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Ren|first=Jiawen|last2=Li|first2=Fang-Fang|last3=Lau|first3=Jason|last4=González-Urbina|first4=Luis|last5=Licht|first5=Stuart|date=2015-08-05|title=One-Pot Synthesis of Carbon Nanofibers from CO2|journal=Nano Letters|volume=15|issue=9|pages=6142–6148|doi=10.1021/acs.nanolett.5b02427|pmid=26237131|bibcode=2015NanoL..15.6142R|doi-access=free}}</ref>其机理与CVD类似。一些金属离子被还原成金属态，并附着在阴极上作为碳纳米管生长的成核点。 阴极上的反应是：

:<chem>Li2CO3 -> Li2O + CNTs + O2</chem>

如方程式所示，所形成的氧化锂可以吸收二氧化碳{{efn|如果反应器中的碳元素产生了二氧化碳}}并形成碳酸锂。

:<chem>Li2O + CO2 -> Li2CO3</chem>

总反应为：

:<chem>CO2 -> CNTs + O2</chem>

换句话说，反应物仅是温室气体中的二氧化碳，而产物却是高价值的碳纳米管。。 科学<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/news/2015/08/carbon-capture-strategy-pays|title=A carbon capture strategy that pays|date=2015-08-19|work=Science|access-date=2018-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129023024/https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2015/08/carbon-capture-strategy-pays|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Service|first=Robert F.|date=2015-09-11|title=Conjuring chemical cornucopias out of thin air|journal=Science|volume=349|issue=6253|pages=1160|doi=10.1126/science.349.6253.1160|pmid=26359385}}</ref>，BBC新闻<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-33998697|title=Carbon fibres made from air|last=Webb|first=Jonathan|date=2015-08-20|work=BBC News|access-date=2018-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103414/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-33998697|dead-url=no}}</ref>，MIT技术新闻<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://hta-net.org/mit-technology-review-researcher-demonstrates-how-to-suck-carbon-from-the-air-make-stuff-from-it/|title=Researcher Demonstrates How to Suck Carbon from the Air, Make Stuff from It|work=MIT Technology Review|access-date=2018-10-26|author=Orcutt, Mike|date=2015-08-19|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203214953/http://hta-net.org/mit-technology-review-researcher-demonstrates-how-to-suck-carbon-from-the-air-make-stuff-from-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，等着重指出了这一发现，并将其视为一种二氧化碳捕获和转化的技术。

=== 火焰环境 ===
[[富勒烯|富勒烯]]和[[碳纳米管|碳纳米管]]不一定是高科技实验室的产品，它们也可在燃烧甲烷<ref>{{cite journal|last=Yuan|first=Liming|year=2001|title=Nanotubes from methane flames|journal=Chemical Physics Letters|volume=340|pages=237–241|doi=10.1016/S0009-2614(01)00435-3|issue=3–4|last2=Saito|first2=Kozo|last3=Pan|first3=Chunxu|last4=Williams|first4=F.A|last5=Gordon|first5=A.S|bibcode = 2001CPL...340..237Y }}</ref>，乙烯<ref>{{cite journal|last=Yuan|first=Liming|year=2001|title=Ethylene flame synthesis of well-aligned multi-walled carbon nanotubes|journal=Chemical Physics Letters|volume=346|pages=23–28|doi=10.1016/S0009-2614(01)00959-9|last2=Saito|first2=Kozo|last3=Hu|first3=Wenchong|last4=Chen|first4=Zhi|bibcode = 2001CPL...346...23Y|issue=1–2}}</ref>，和苯<ref>{{cite journal|last=Duan|first=H. M.|year=1994|title=Nanoclusters Produced in Flames|journal=Journal of Physical Chemistry|volume=98|pages=12815–12818|doi=10.1021/j100100a001|last2=McKinnon|first2=J. T.|issue=49}}</ref>产生的普通[[火焰|火焰]]中形成<ref>{{Cite journal|first=J.M.|last=Singer|title=Carbon formation in very rich hydrocarbon-air flames. I. Studies of chemical content, temperature, ionization and particulate matter|journal=Seventh Symposium (International) on Combustion|year=1959}}</ref>，在室内和室外空气的烟灰中也发现了它们。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Murr|first=L. E.|year=2004|title=Carbon nanotubes, nanocrystal forms, and complex nanoparticle aggregates in common fuel-gas combustion sources and the ambient air|journal=Journal of Nanoparticle Research|volume=6|pages=241–251|doi=10.1023/B:NANO.0000034651.91325.40|last2=Bang|first2=J.J.|last3=Esquivel|first3=E.V.|last4=Guerrero|first4=P.A.|last5=Lopez|first5=D.A.|issue=2/3|bibcode=2004JNR.....6..241M}}</ref>但是，这些天然存在的品种在尺寸和质量上可能是极不规则的，因为它们的生产环境高度不受控。<ref>{{Cite journal|first=A.V.|last=Saveliev|title=Metal catalyzed synthesis of carbon nanostructures in an opposed flow methane oxygen flame|doi=10.1016/S0010-2180(03)00142-1|journal=Combust. Flame|volume=135|pages=27–33|year=2003|last2=Merchan-Merchan|first2=Wilson|last3=Kennedy|first3=Lawrence A.|issue=1–2}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|first=M.J.|last=Height|title=Flame synthesis of single-walled carbon nanotubes|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_carbon_2004_42_11/page/2295|doi=10.1016/j.carbon.2004.05.010|journal=Carbon|volume=42|pages=2295–2307|year=2004|issue=11|last2=Howard|first2=Jack B.|last3=Tester|first3=Jefferson W.|last4=Vander Sande|first4=John B.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|first=S.|last=Sen|title=Flame synthesis of carbon nanofibers and nanofibers composites containing encapsulated metal particles|journal=Nanotechnology|volume=15|pages=264–268|year=2004|doi=10.1088/0957-4484/15/3/005|last2=Puri|first2=Ishwar K|issue=3|bibcode = 2004Nanot..15..264S }}</ref> 因此，尽管它们可以在某些应用中使用，但是它们可能缺乏研究和工业所必需的高度均匀性。研究人员的努力主要在于控制火焰的环境以生产理化性质更均匀的碳纳米管。<ref>{{Cite journal|first=R.L.|last=Vander Wal|title=Fe-catalyzed single-walled carbon nanotube synthesis within a flame environment|journal=Combust. Flame|volume=130|pages=37–47|year=2002|doi=10.1016/S0010-2180(02)00360-7|issue=1–2}}</ref>基于理论模型，这种方法有希望进行大规模、低成本的纳米管合成，尽管它们必须与快速发展的大规模[[化学气相沉积|化学气相沉积]]竞争。<ref>{{Cite journal|author1=Naha, Sayangdev |author2=Sen, Swarnendu |author3=De, Anindya K. |author4=Puri, Ishwar K. |title=A detailed model for the Flame synthesis of carbon nanotubes and nanofibers|journal=Proceedings of the Combustion Institute|volume=31|issue=2|pages=1821–29|doi=10.1016/j.proci.2006.07.224|year=2007}}</ref>

